01:29:10,445 --> 01:29:27,371
shall within 45 days review said application, make recommendations as it deems appropriate and send copies thereof to the city council or board of appeals and to the applicant failure of the board to make recommendations within 45 days of receipt by said board of the application shall be deemed lack of opposition thereto.

